  Goa2 chai in e5 hong5-chui2 e5 kou3-su7 u7 m7-tioh8, sou2-i2 goa2 chiu7 eng7 in e5 ji7 in3 chit pun2 “Na2-a e5 toa7-chui2” hou7 in thak8. (Bi7-oan5)
